.Xr strpbrk 3 ,
.Xr strrchr 3 ,
.Xr strsep 3 ,
.Xr strstr 3 ,
.Xr strtok 3 ,
.Xr wcsspn 3
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Fn strspn
function conforms to
.St -ansiC .
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Fn strspn
function first appeared in
.At III
and was reimplemented for
.Bx 4.3 .
